            <dd class="accordion-content accordionItem is-collapsed" id="accordion1" aria-hidden="true">
                <p>In order to provide an effective ant control you must know what you are dealing with.  I
                start by surveying your property to determine what type of ants are present, where they
                are and what level of infestation exists.</p>

                <p>The next step is to develop a treatment plan.  My customized treatments take care of
                the immediate problems as well as treat ant harborage sites in the landscape to prevent
                future population growth.</p>

                <p>
                    For more information about Ant Control visit: <br />
