                    My treatment for cockroaches is very thorough and effective and consist of a three phase
                    approach: Inspect, Remove and Treat.  Following a thorough inspection I will identify the species
                    and come up with an effective plan to treat the infestation.  Treatments are sold based on the
                    level of infestation and may require multiple treatments
                </p>

