            </dt>
            <dd class="accordion-content accordionItem is-collapsed" id="accordion13" aria-hidden="true">
                <p>Snake removal is a specialty service. Upland Pest Control understands that a snake in the home is an emergency that cannot wait.  That is why 
                emergency snake removal is available. Snake removal can be dangerous and should only be done by a trained professional.  In most cases unwanted 
